      <title>Fcitx5 for Macos</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/2026/02/fcitx5-for-macos/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Feb 2026 11:44:19 +0700</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/2026/02/fcitx5-for-macos/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;installation&#34;&gt;Installation&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/fcitx/fcitx5-macos&#34;&gt;github&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;lệnh tải &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/fcitx-contrib/fcitx5-macos-installer/blob/master/README.zh-CN.md&#34;&gt;url&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;cd /tmp &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; rm -rf Fcitx5Installer.app &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; curl -LO https://github.com/fcitx-contrib/fcitx5-macos-installer/releases/download/latest/Fcitx5Installer.zip &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; unzip Fcitx5Installer.zip &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; open Fcitx5Installer.app
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h1 id=&#34;pros-and-cons&#34;&gt;Pros and cons&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Instead of using tools like Unikey, EVKey, or Bamboo, using Fcitx5 feels more native. It is similar to the built-in macOS keyboard, allowing you to switch languages using the default macOS keyboard shortcuts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
